'''Karfeddion Spaceport''' was a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] on planet [[Karfeddion/Legends|Karfeddion]]. It was filled with [[Hangar/Legends|hangars]], [[Starship/Legends|starship]] repair businesses and shady [[Cantina/Legends|cantinas]].

One of its many docking bays was [[Docking Bay 331]] where mercenary [[Arwen Cohl]] and his crew [[Boiny]] and [[Lope (individual)|Lope]] rendezvoused with several [[Nebula Front/Legends|Nebula Front]] members in [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]].

